translate portuguese tolawoffices_305d4eac:

    # ss "Still, that's crazy!"
    ss "Mesmo assim, isso é de loucos!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:495
translate portuguese tolawoffices_e7c8842f:

    # ss "So they just hired you on the spot? "
    ss "Então contrataram-te na hora? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:496
translate portuguese tolawoffices_a76ed944:

    # pc "Yep, I got the job."
    pc "Sim, consegui o emprego."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:497
translate portuguese tolawoffices_de6bcecf:

    # ss "How? I had like three girlfriends who applied for that same job and never got a call back. "
    ss "Como? Tinha tipo três amigas que se candidataram ao mesmo emprego e nunca receberam resposta. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:498
translate portuguese tolawoffices_9a021f76:

    # pc "Really? "
    pc "A sério? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:499
translate portuguese tolawoffices_96260a19:

    # ss "Yeah, they said that the woman didn't even seem interested in hiring them. What did you do to get that job? "
    ss "Sim, disseram que a mulher nem parecia interessada em contratá-las. O que fizeste para conseguires esse emprego? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:500
translate portuguese tolawoffices_e9d53d74:

    # pc "Just walked in and asked for it. "
    pc "Simplesmente entrei e pedi-o. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:501
translate portuguese tolawoffices_7886c317:

    # ss "Didn't perform any favors then? "
    ss "Não fizeste nenhum favor, então? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:502
translate portuguese tolawoffices_1abd5f9d:

    # pc "What? No! Don't be gross. "
    pc "O quê? Não! Não sejas nojenta. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:503
translate portuguese tolawoffices_b2859774:

    # ss "Alright, sure. If you say so. "
    ss "Tudo bem, claro. Se o dizes. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:504
translate portuguese tolawoffices_578ec521:

    # "She looks at me suspiciously. "
    "Ela olha para mim com desconfiança. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:505
translate portuguese tolawoffices_31bab525:

    # "I reach into her car and take out my bag that has the cell phone in it. "
    "Estico-me para dentro do carro dela e tiro a minha mala, onde está o telemóvel. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:506
translate portuguese tolawoffices_ed0d368e:

    # pc "Well, I'll see you at home. Thanks again for driving me around today. "
    pc "Bem, vejo-te em casa. Obrigado mais uma vez por me teres levado hoje. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:509
translate portuguese tolawoffices_65fdee3e:

    # ss "Hey you still owe me gas money!"
    ss "Ei, ainda me deves o dinheiro da gasolina!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:510
translate portuguese tolawoffices_e902b56c:

    # pc "Oh yeah, sorry. Will $10 do?"
    pc "Ah, sim, desculpa. 10 dólares dá?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:511
translate portuguese tolawoffices_87ff94f5:

    # ss "That's fine."
    ss "Está bem."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:513
translate portuguese tolawoffices_1b7e7694:

    # "I hand her a ten from the little amount of money I have in my wallet."
    "Entreguei-lhe uma nota de dez do pouco dinheiro que tinha na carteira."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:514
translate portuguese tolawoffices_70e27b89:

    # ss "Alright, see you later."
    ss "Tudo bem, até logo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:517
translate portuguese tolawoffices_98bddef0:

    # ss "Yeah, yeah. See you later. "
    ss "Sim, sim. Até logo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:520
translate portuguese tolawoffices_afba32b7:

    # "She pulls out quickly and cuts off two people as she drives onto the busy road in front of the law offices. "
    "Ela arranca rapidamente e ultrapassa duas pessoas ao entrar na estrada movimentada em frente ao escritório de advogados. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:521
translate portuguese tolawoffices_3e9feed9:

    # "I walk over to one of the company cars. They both look exactly the same – generic black sedans, a few years old, with slightly tinted windows."
    "Dirijo-me a um dos carros da empresa. São ambos idênticos – sedans pretos genéricos, com alguns anos, com vidros ligeiramente escurecidos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:522
translate portuguese tolawoffices_c65d2d31:

    # "I press the unlock button on the key fob and one of the cars beeps. I open the driver's side door and get inside."
    "Carrego no botão de desbloqueio do comando e um dos carros emite um sinal sonoro. Abro a porta do lado do condutor e entro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:525
translate portuguese tolawoffices_762489ab:

    # "The inside of the car is clean and smells a bit musty as if it hasn't been used for a while."
    "O interior do carro está limpo e cheira um pouco a mofo, como se não fosse usado há algum tempo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:526
translate portuguese tolawoffices_76a7ccb7:

    # "It is simple and not very flashy, but it will get me around until I can buy a car of my own."
    "É simples e não muito chamativo, mas vai servir para me deslocar até eu poder comprar um carro próprio."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:527
translate portuguese tolawoffices_07e0ebfc:

    # "Actually, it is probably better than any car that I'd ever owned. I'd only had one car before - an old junker that my dad had gotten me."
    "Na verdade, é provavelmente melhor do que qualquer carro que eu já tenha tido. Eu só tinha tido um carro antes – uma velha sucata que o meu pai me tinha arranjado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:528
translate portuguese tolawoffices_ff0881b6:

    # "It barely ran and needed constant work. I sold it off before going to Brazil. Then down there, I didn't have any form of transportation. I just walked everywhere. "
    "Mal funcionava e precisava de reparações constantes. Vendi-o antes de ir para o Brasil. Depois, lá, não tinha qualquer meio de transporte. Andava a pé para todo o lado. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:529
translate portuguese tolawoffices_076df576:

    # "The car starts as soon as I turn the key, and once I back out onto the street it drives perfectly fine. It doesn't have much power, but enough to get me from place to place."
    "O carro arranca assim que giro a chave e, assim que saio para a rua, anda na perfeição. Não tem muita potência, mas o suficiente para me levar de um sítio para outro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:530
translate portuguese tolawoffices_61f7e0fb:

    # "I would have taken the job even without the car, but now, not having to rely on somebody else to drive me around is the best feeling. "
    "Teria aceitado o emprego mesmo sem o carro, mas agora, não ter de depender de outra pessoa para me levar de um lado para o outro é a melhor sensação. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:531
translate portuguese tolawoffices_5ba209a0:

    # "It's evening now. I have a little time left to do some things before heading home for the night, and I have the means to go anywhere I want."
    "Já é noite. Ainda tenho algum tempo para fazer algumas coisas antes de voltar para casa, e tenho meios para ir aonde quiser."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:532
translate portuguese tolawoffices_f228727e:

    # "I suddenly remember the park that I used to play at when I was younger and I wonder what it looks like now."
    "De repente, lembro-me do parque onde costumava brincar quando era mais novo e pergunto-me como estará agora."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:533
translate portuguese tolawoffices_cfe242e6:

    # "There are plenty of places to go, and I have plenty of time to check out that park later. Where do I want to go NOW?"
    "Há muitos sítios para onde ir, e tenho tempo de sobra para visitar aquele parque mais tarde. Onde é que quero ir AGORA?"

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:219
    old "What's wrong with us being in the same class?"
    new "O que há de errado em estarmos na mesma turma?"

    # game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:221
    old "I hope so too. That would be horrible."
    new "Também espero que sim. Isso seria horrível."

